@page "/ML/Intro"

<MudContainer MaxWidth="MaxWidth.Medium" Class="mx-auto my-8">
<MudText Typo="Typo.h4">Machine Learning</MudText>
<MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle1" Class="mb-8">
    Machine Learning uses past data to make predictions about the future. It's a powerful tool for pattern recognition.
</MudText>

<MudExpansionPanels class="mt-4" MultiExpansion="false">
    <MudExpansionPanel Text="What is Machine Learning?" Expanded="true">
        <MudText Typo="Typo.h5">What is Machine Learning?</MudText>
        <MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle1" Class="mb-4">
            Machine Learning is a way to use historical data or relationships in data to make predictions about the future.
        </MudText>

        <img src="MLStudying.png" alt="A robot studying" style="height: 600px; width: auto;" class="mt-4">
    </MudExpansionPanel>
    <MudExpansionPanel Text="What do I mean by data?">
        <MudText Typo="Typo.h5">What is Training Data?</MudText>
        <MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle1" Class="mb-4">
            Training Data is information that we can use to make predictions.
        </MudText>

        <img src="MLHomework.png" alt="A homework set of grades" style="height: auto; width: 100%;" class="mt-4">
    </MudExpansionPanel>
    <MudExpansionPanel Text="Example: Sleeping In">
        <MudText Typo="Typo.h5">Predicting Car Defrosting Time</MudText>
        <MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle1" Class="mb-4">
            Matt might like to sleep in so much that he built a machine learning model to predict how long it will take to defrost his car.
        </MudText>

        <img src="Defrost.png" alt="Matt defrosting his car" style="height: 600px; width: auto;" class="mt-4">
    </MudExpansionPanel>
    <MudExpansionPanel Text="Example: Running Museum HVACs">
        <MudText Typo="Typo.h5">Controlling heating, ventilation and air conditioning at museums</MudText>
        <MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle1" Class="mb-4">
            Sam helped a museum save money by predicting when to turn on and off their HVAC systems.
        </MudText>

        <img src="Museum.png" alt="Sam coding a thermostat" style="height: 600px; width: auto;" class="mt-4">
    </MudExpansionPanel>
    <MudExpansionPanel Text="Example: World Peace">
        <MudText Typo="Typo.h5">Is Die Hard a Christmas Movie?</MudText>
        <MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle1" Class="mb-4">
            Matt got into a disagreement on whether or not Die Hard should be considered a Christmas movie. He built a machine learning model to solve the debate.
        </MudText>

        <img src="DieHard.png" alt="Matt's content on Die Hard" style="height: 600px; width: auto;" class="mt-4">
    </MudExpansionPanel>
    <MudExpansionPanel Text="Example: Making TV Shows Good">
        <MudText Typo="Typo.h5">Predicting Episode Ratings for Doctor Who</MudText>
        <MudText Typo="Typo.subtitle1" Class="mb-4">
            Matt might like Doctor Who so much that he built a machine learning model to predict how good an episode will be - in order to help make the show actually good again.
        </MudText>

        <img src="DoctorWho.jpeg" alt="Matt working on Doctor Who Data" style="height: 600px; width: auto;" class="mt-4">
    </MudExpansionPanel>
</MudExpansionPanels>
</MudContainer>